{"type": "article", "id": 22623, "title": "布丁沙发", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-22T10:45:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702104005dOQS4ZljFqeAB2E5.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是有所品牌推出的一款想让人联想到“布丁”的沙发，亮丽的黄色配合有些拟人化的设计让沙发显得甜美可爱。两边的扶手和沙发上的垫子都是圆柱形的，偶尔采用棕色的仿皮面料作为反差，增加了光泽感。细木腿的使用也突出了沙发的主体，显得柔软舒适。另有一款绿色的“抹茶布丁”，售价 2850 元，<a href=\"https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.1-c.w5003-11731905043.4.fBw1zJ&amp;id=521830547590&amp;scene=taobao_shop\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104003TUn8Qxzl9paSPetv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px; height: 562px; width: 375px; left: 519px; top: 426px;\" class=\"dragged\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104003sWVLxPGvJmkOaqzK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104004atG5VuOoP6zlUJIb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104004TljeX9HtkaB0vrs1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}